metadata.name: Keep Watch Crew #1
metadata.description: The Keep Watch Crew (KWC) is a collection of 6,969 one-of-a-kind Keep Watch eyeball NFTs. Each one is unique and as the name states, collecting this project makes you a member of the Keep Watch Crew. Apart from having your very own individual Keep Watch, you will be a part of the next chapter of Mishka - a voyage into the MISHKAVERSE and all the perks that come with a membership.
